### Auth - Usuario autenticado Ana
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Auth - Usuario autenticado sin token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

### Auth - Usuario autenticado con token invalido
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token


### Projects - Crear proyecto como Ana
POST {{baseUrl}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Project Alpha",
  "description": "Initial description"
}

### Projects - Crear proyecto sin descripcion
POST {{baseUrl}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Project Without Description"
}

### Projects - Crear proyecto sin token
POST {{baseUrl}}/project
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Unauthorized Project",
  "description": "This request should fail without a bearer token"
}

### Projects - Listar proyectos accesibles como Ana
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Projects - Listar proyectos accesibles como Bob
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### Projects - Listar proyectos sin token
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects

### Projects - Consultar detalle como Ana
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Projects - Consultar detalle como Bob antes de grant
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### Projects - Consultar detalle sin token
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info

### Projects - Actualizar nombre y descripcion
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Project Alpha Updated",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Projects - Actualizar solo descripcion a null
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": null
}

### Projects - Actualizar con cuerpo vacio
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Projects - Actualizar sin token
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/info
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Unauthorized Update"
}


### Project invites - Otorgar acceso participant a Bob
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/invite?user=bob
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project invites - Otorgar acceso participant a Carla
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/invite?user=carla
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project invites - Usuario inexistente
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/invite?user=missing-user
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project invites - Otorgar acceso sin token
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/invite?user=bob


### Project members - Listar miembros como Ana
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project members - Listar miembros como Bob despues de grant
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### Project members - Listar miembros como Carla owner despues de grant
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{carlaToken}}

### Project members - Listar miembros sin token
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members

### Project members - Quitar participant Bob como Ana
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members/{{bobUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project members - Quitar owner Ana debe devolver 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members/1
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project members - Quitar owner Carla debe devolver 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members/{{carlaUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}

### Project members - Quitar miembro como Bob debe devolver 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members/{{bobUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### Project members - Quitar miembro sin token
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/members/{{bobUserId}}


### Documents - Subir PDF como Ana
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ProjectVaultBoundary

--ProjectVaultBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

%PDF-1.7
ProjectVault test PDF content
--ProjectVaultBoundary--

### Documents - Subir DOCX como Ana
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ProjectVaultBoundary

--ProjectVaultBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="brief.docx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document

ProjectVault test DOCX content
--ProjectVaultBoundary--

### Documents - Subir TXT debe devolver 415
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ProjectVaultBoundary

--ProjectVaultBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="notes.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Plain text is not supported
--ProjectVaultBoundary--

### Documents - Subir PDF con content_type incorrecto debe devolver 415
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ProjectVaultBoundary

--ProjectVaultBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="wrong-content-type.pdf"
Content-Type: text/plain

This filename is PDF but content type is text/plain
--ProjectVaultBoundary--

### Documents S3 - Pedir URL presignada de upload PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/documents/presign-upload
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "contract.pdf",
  "content_type": "application/pdf"
}

### Documents S3 - Subir objeto con URL presignada
PUT {{presignedUploadUrl}}
Content-Type: application/pdf

%PDF-1.7
ProjectVault S3-compatible PDF content

### Documents S3 - Completar upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/documents/complete-upload
Authorization: Bearer {{anaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_id": {{presignedDocumentId}}
}

